<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hellish" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hellish,</orth> 1) pertaining to hell, devilish, infernal: <bibl n="shak. mv 3.4.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 4, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 4, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.485" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 485</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.368" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 368</bibl>.<lb />2) wicked: <cit><quote>only sin and h. obstinacy tie thy tongue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.186" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 186</bibl></cit>.
